alt: woman looking to her side with a straight black bob and bangs, she is looking into the sunset and it's casting light and shadows all over her face
description:
2024 

This is a redo of an old watercolor I did in 2019. It has been hanging in a sunny room, and was not super bold to begin with, so it is pretty faded by now. I used a new, but similar reference with the same theme and focused on creating really bold colors. I wanted everything to pop and I'm really happy with it.
